The National Drug Law Enforcement Agency says it arrested a comedian, Sunday Martins, because drugs were found at his house. Martins, a Nigerian skit maker better known as De General, was arrested by NDLEA operatives at his house in Lagos on Wednesday.  A video, which went viral on Wednesday, showed officials assaulting a comedian in a viral video. See Also






